style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 나눔명조; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 나눔명조; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">)</span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 나눔명조;\">에 수좌스님들의 묵언정진을 지지하며 재가불자 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 나눔명조; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 나눔명조; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">108</span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 나눔명조;\">배 수행정진을 시작했습니다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 나눔명조; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 나눔명조; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">.</span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 150%; text-indent: 13pt; margin-top: 4pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 나눔명조;\">지금까지 교단자정센터 김종규 원장이 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 나눔명조; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 나눔명조; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">7</span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 나눔명조;\">일째 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 나눔명조; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 나눔명조; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">108</span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 나눔명조;\">배 수행정진을 하고 있으며</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 나눔명조; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 나눔명조; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 나눔명조;\">더 많은 불자들이 함께할 것입니다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 나눔명조; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 나눔명조; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">.</span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 150%; text-indent: 13pt; margin-top: 4pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 나눔명조;\">또한</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 나눔명조; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 나눔명조; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 나눔명조;\">오늘 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 나눔명조; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 나눔명조; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">9</span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 나눔명조;\">월 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 나눔명조; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 나눔명조; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">6</span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 나눔명조;\">일</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 나눔명조; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 나눔명조; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">(</span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 나눔명조;\">금요일</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 나눔명조; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 나눔명조; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">)</span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 나눔명조;\">은 수행정진 후 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 나눔명조; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 나눔명조; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">\"</span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 나눔명조;\">재가연대와 함께하는 작은 음악회</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 나눔명조; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 나눔명조; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">\"</span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 나눔명조;\">가 열립니다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 나눔명조; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 나눔명조; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">. </span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 나눔명조;\">많은 관심과 동참을 바랍니다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 나눔명조; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 나눔명조; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">.</span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 150%; text-indent: 13pt; margin-top: 4pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 나눔명조; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 나눔명조; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">“</span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 나눔명조;\">수좌스님들을 지지하는 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 나눔명조; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 나눔명조; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">108</span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-fa