: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"480\" src=\"http://cfile24.uf.tistory.com/image/25298F3A525363BB29172C\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;\"><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"480\" src=\"http://cfile10.uf.tistory.com/image/256E0838525363BD307B32\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;\"><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"480\" src=\"http://cfile28.uf.tistory.com/image/23044F36525363BF33A8B9\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;\"><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"480\" src=\"http://cfile7.uf.tistory.com/image/247F053B525365AA279269\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;\"><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"480\" src=\"http://cfile3.uf.tistory.com/image/213DDE36525365B112CEA0\"></span></p>", visible: false, anonymous: false},
  {intab_id: 9, author_name: "관리자", author_id: 1, author_passwd: "bsr213417", title: "청정승가 구현을 위한 재가불자 용맹정진(9/26~30)", file1: nil, file2: nil, ir1: "<br><p>청정승가 구현을 위한 재가불자 용맹정진</p><p>9월 26일 108배 수행정진</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;\"><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"480\" src=\"http://cfile5.uf.tistory.com/image/243A7436525366E21CB5D6\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;\"><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"480\" src=\"http://cfile10.uf.tistory.com/image/2424E535525366E30C545D\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;\">&nbsp;<span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"480\" src=\"http://cfile24.uf.tistory.com/image/2644CE38525366E50E8BC0\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>9월 27일 108배 수행정진</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;\"><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"480\" src=\"http://cfile5.uf.tistory.com/image/261DD63952536832056D38\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;\"><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"480\" src=\"http://cfile22.uf.tistory.com/image/27162D395253683309EDB5\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;\"><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"480\" src=\"http://cfile30.uf.tistory.com/image/220AFA395253683512D20D\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;\"><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"480\" src=\"http://cfile5.uf.tistory.com/image/2323EC39525368350186B3\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;\"><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"480\" src=\"http://cfile22.uf.tistory.com/image/222D053C525366E82F36BF\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;\">&nbsp;</p><p>9월 28~29일 철야정진 (29일 새벽 3시 현재, 불교여성개발원 법당)<br>- 9월 28일(토) 저녁 포살법회 때부터 폭우가 찾아와 천막 안에서도 비에 젖는 상황이 되었습니다.<br>- 이에 저녁 9시 30분에 불교여성개발원 법당으로&nbsp;이전한 후에 새벽 5시까지 철야정진을 했습니다.</p><p style=\"text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;\"><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"480\" src=\"http://cfile22.uf.tistory.com/image/252CDA3C525366E92E0ABD\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;\"><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"480\" src=\"http://cfile22.uf.tistory.com/image/2126E13C525366E932817F\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;\"><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"480\" src=\"http://cfile25.uf.tistory.com/image/242DBC3C525366EA3385CE\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;\"><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"480\" src=\"http://cfile8.uf.tistory.com/image/24162A38525366EB2C9E47\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;\"><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"480\" src=\"http://cfile29.uf.tistory.com/image/273A7338525366EC14E7BE\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;\"><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"480\" src=\"http://cfile23.uf.tistory.com/image/24059338525366EC35D01E\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>9월 29일 108배 수행정진</p><p style=\"text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;\"><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"480\" src=\"http://cfile28.uf.tistory.com/image/2741753C525366EE239A33\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;\"><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"480\" src=\"http://cfile2.uf.tistory.com/image/232B5A3C525366EF30E340\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>9월 30일 108배 수행정진</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;\"><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"480\" src=\"http://cfile27.uf.tistory.com/image/2231D63C525366EF2C178D\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;\"><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"480\" src=\"http://cfile5.uf.tistory.com/image/2405B43B525369A636981F\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;\"><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"480\" src=\"http://cfile8.uf.tistory.com/image/2105603B525369BC35C0D5\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;\"><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"480\" src=\"http://cfile7.uf.tistory.com/image/27158D3B525369C12D11CA\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;\"><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"480\" src=\"http://cfile27.uf.tistory.com/image/2618BD3A525369C307A262\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;\"><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"480\" src=\"http://cfile21.uf.tistory.com/image/2749823B525369C411744B\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;\"><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"480\" src=\"http://cfile7.uf.tistory.com/image/221C5337525369C6355937\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;\"><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"480\" src=\"http://cfile26.uf.tistory.com/image/23630637525369C608EB55\"></span></p>", visible: false, anonymous: false},
  {intab_id: 9, author_name: "관리자", author_id: 1, author_passwd: "bsr213417", title: "41일간의 108배정진과 철야용맹정진을 회향하며", file1: nil, file2: nil, ir1: "<!--StartFragment--><p class=\"0\" style=\"-ms-layout-grid-mode: both; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">재가불자여</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">!! </span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">우리가 부처입니다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">. </span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">희망을 버리지 맙시다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">.</span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"-ms-layout-grid-mode: both; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">-41</span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">일 간의 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">108</span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">배 정진과 철야 용맹정진을 회향하며</span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"-ms-layout-grid-mode: both; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"> <!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]--> <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"-ms-layout-grid-mode: both; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">1. 41</span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">일 간의 정진을 회향합니다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">.</span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"-ms-layout-grid-mode: both; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"> <!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]--> <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"-ms-layout-grid-mode: both; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">자승 스님의 총무원장 당선을 축하드리고 개혁에 힘쓰시길 간구합니다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">.</span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"-ms-layout-grid-mode: both; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"> <!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]--> <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"-ms-layout-grid-mode: both; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">우리 재가불자들의 눈에는 도저히 종단의 미래가 보이지 않습니다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">.</span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"-ms-layout-grid-mode: both; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">현재 일부 스님들의 권력 다툼과 범계</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">폭력 등으로 위대한 우리불교는 사라져 보이지 않는 것 같습니다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">.</span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"-ms-layout-grid-mode: both; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"> <!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]--> <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"-ms-layout-grid-mode: both; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">이 땅의 불자들이 스님들과 더불어 매도당하고</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">이 땅의 어머니들이 눈물로 밤을 지새우고</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">이 땅의 젊은이들이 경쟁사회의 희생양으로 널브러져 있어도</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">이 땅의 민주주의가 짓이겨지는 상황이 발생하여도 출가자들은 이 땅의 민초들을 위한 우산을 받쳐 들고 보살필 생각을 하지 않고 있습니다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">.</span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"-ms-layout-grid-mode: both; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"> <!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]--> <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"-ms-layout-grid-mode: both; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">오히려 총무원장 선거를 통해 약속 위반과 권력 다툼을 위한 스님들의 아우성과 반칙을 목도하였을 뿐 정법을 구현하기 위한 커다란 움직임은 어디에도 보이지 않습니다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">.</span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"-ms-layout-grid-mode: both; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"> <!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]--> <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"-ms-layout-grid-mode: both; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">이전 수좌회 스님들이 용맹정진을 풀고 조계사를 떠났고</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">지금은 저희들이 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">41</span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">일 간의 정진을 풀고 조계종 총무원 앞 우정총국 공원을 떠나지만</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">다음에는 전국의 천만 불자들이 종단을 떠날 것입니다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">.</span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"-ms-layout-grid-mode: both; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"> <!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]--> <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"-ms-layout-grid-mode: both; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">2. </span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">그 동안 승가에 기대었고</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">참다운 재가자들의 모습을 구현하기 위한 노력을 등한시 하였던 점을 참회합니다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">.</span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"-ms-layout-grid-mode: both; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"> <!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]--> <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"-ms-layout-grid-mode: both; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">재가자들이 우리의 위대한 불교를 이 땅에 현신하도록 하여야 합니다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">.</span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"-ms-layout-grid-mode: both; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"> <!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]--> <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"-ms-layout-grid-mode: both; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">신자들의 수준이 곧 성직자의 수준입니다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">.</span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"-ms-layout-grid-mode: both; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"> <!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]--> <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"-ms-layout-grid-mode: both; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">석가세존을 떠나게 만든 꼬삼비의 비구들에 대한 꼬삼비의 재가자들 행동처럼 거룩하지 못한 출가자들에게는 절하지 말고</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">보고도 일어나지 말고</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">합장의 예를 갖추지 말고</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">존중하지 말고</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">공경하지 말고</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">봉사하지 말고</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">공양 올리지 않는다면</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">우리의 위대한 불교는 맑고 향기로운 교단을 통해 이 땅에 현신할 것입니다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">.</span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"-ms-layout-grid-mode: both; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"> <!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]--> <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"-ms-layout-grid-mode: both; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">자정센터는 참다운 재가자의 모습을 구현하기 위한 모든 노력을 다할 것입니다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">.</span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"-ms-layout-grid-mode: both; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"> <!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]--> <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"-ms-layout-grid-mode: both; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"> <!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]--> <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"-ms-layout-grid-mode: both; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">3. </span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">개개의 사안에 대한 자정활동 치중하기보다는 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">10</span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">년을 내다보고 청정과 화합하는 승단과 사부대중 공동체를 만들기 위하여 노력하겠습니다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">.</span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"-ms-layout-grid-mode: both; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"> <!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]--> <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"-ms-layout-grid-mode: both; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">거룩하지 못한 출가자를 굶기고</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">앞으로 인천의 사표가 될 출가자와 재가자를 지원</span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">ㆍ</span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">육성하여 청정교단의 당간을 세울 수 있다면 그리 할 것입니다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">.</span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"-ms-layout-grid-mode: both; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"> <!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]--> <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"-ms-layout-grid-mode: both; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">출가자들은 삼보정재와 공양 받은 음식물이 신도들로부터 나온다는 것을 분명히 인식하여야 하며</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">신자들은 자신의 공양이 거룩한 스승을 만드는 데에만 사용되어야 함을 분명히 인식하여야 합니다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">.</span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"-ms-layout-grid-mode: both; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"> <!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]--> <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"-ms-layout-grid-mode: both; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">자정센터는 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">10</span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">년을 내다보고 거룩하지 못한 행위를 하는 출가자에게는 분명히 후과가 있음을 명심시킬 것이며</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">재가자 법회와 온라인</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">오프라인 활동을 통하여 재가자들의 의식을 향상시킬 것이며</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">거룩한 스승과 훌륭한 재가활동가가 될 수 있는 분들에 대하여는 여러 가지 지원 활동을 모색할 것입니다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">.</span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"-ms-layout-grid-mode: both; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"> <!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]--> <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"-ms-layout-grid-mode: both; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">4. </span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">재가불자들 여러분들이 희망입니다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">.</span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"-ms-layout-grid-mode: both; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"> <!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]--> <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"-ms-layout-grid-mode: both; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">말법시대와도 같아 보이는 이러한 어려운 시기는 오히려 재가불자들이 깨어날 수 있는 좋은 기회입니다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">.</span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"-ms-layout-grid-mode: both; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"> <!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]--> <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"-ms-layout-grid-mode: both; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">힘을 모아 승가에 기댐이 없이 재가불자들의 참모습을 찾아간다면 출재가 모두가 깨어나 청정하고 화합하는 승단을 만들 수 있습니다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">.</span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"-ms-layout-grid-mode: both; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"> <!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]--> <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"-ms-layout-grid-mode: both; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">재가불자여</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">!! </span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">우리가 부처입니다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">. </span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">희망을 버리지 맙시다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">.</span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"text-align: center; -ms-layout-grid-mode: both; -ms-word-break: keep-all; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"> <!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]--> <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"text-align: center; -ms-layout-grid-mode: both; -ms-word-break: keep-all; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">불기 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">2557(2013)</span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">년 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">10</span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">월 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 바탕; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">10</span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">일</span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"text-align: center; -ms-layout-grid-mode: both; -ms-word-break: keep-all; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 바탕;\">참여불교재가연대 교단자정센터</span></p>", visible: false, anonymous: false},
  {intab_id: 9, author_name: "관리자", author_id: 1, author_passwd: "bsr213417", title: "10월 10일(목) 108배 수행정진과 철야 용맹정진 회향", file1: nil, file2: nil, ir1: "<p><strong><font size=\"3\">10월 10일(목) 108배 수행정진과 철야 용맹정진 회향</font></strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><font face=\"맑은 고딕\">지난 40여일간의 재가불자 108배 수행정진과 철야 용맹정진은&nbsp;10월 10일(목) 저녁 회향을 하면서 마무리 되었습니다.</font>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: left; clear: none; float: none;\">10월 10일 아침, 주변에 현수막을 설치했습니다.</p><p><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"428\" src=\"http://cfile28.uf.tistory.com/image/22193D48525C9CB13AAFEC\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"428\" src=\"http://cfile23.uf.tistory.com/image/2646E448525C9CB2254B07\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>10월 10일 아침 10시, 일찍 오신 재가불자분들이 먼저 108배 수행정진을 시작했습니다.</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"428\" src=\"http://cfile30.uf.tistory.com/image/22738B48525C9CB407B533\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>오전 11시 부터는 매 시간마다 108배 수행정진을 했습니다.</p><p><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"428\" src=\"http://cfile1.uf.tistory.com/image/2532D750525C9CB828288B\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>자정센터에서&nbsp;오전에&nbsp;만들어온 현수막입니다.</p><p><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"428\" src=\"http://cfile27.uf.tistory.com/image/2204F44B525C9CBA31B244\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>마곡사 스님들이 오셔서 걸어놓은 현수막입니다. 몇번을 옮겨달아야했던 현수막이였습니다.</p><p><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"428\" src=\"http://cfile10.uf.tistory.com/image/273FCA4B525C9CBB0C7CA0\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>청정승가를 기원하는 마음을 총무원장 선거인단 스님들께 전달하고자 마이크를 잡았습니다.</p><p><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"428\" src=\"http://cfile1.uf.tistory.com/image/214A9A50525C9CBE1CA661\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"428\" src=\"http://cfile28.uf.tistory.com/image/26407E50525C9CBF225E7F\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>폭풍전야의 대치 국면&nbsp;같은데요. 현장 분위기는 생각처럼 위압적이지는 않았습니다.</p><p><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"428\" src=\"http://cfile27.uf.tistory.com/image/27526147525C9CC111A9FA\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>호법부에서 선거 중이니 뒤로 물러나 줄 것을 부탁했습니다.</p><p><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"428\" src=\"http://cfile2.uf.tistory.com/image/235AF347525C9CC40B0A4C\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>뒤로 물러나서 다시한번 청정승가를 기원하는 마음을 전달했습니다.</p><p><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"428\" src=\"http://cfile29.uf.tistory.com/image/22669749525CA03A1CBC87\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"428\" src=\"http://cfile29.uf.tistory.com/image/23060D50525CA03D070EE2\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"428\" src=\"http://cfile23.uf.tistory.com/image/25469B50525CA03F30D5C1\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>108배 수행정진과 철야 용맹정진 회향</p><p><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"428\" src=\"http://cfile25.uf.tistory.com/image/22050350525CA040080000\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"428\" src=\"http://cfile3.uf.tistory.com/image/24565347525CA3A732E59D\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>성명서 낭독</p><p><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"428\" src=\"http://cfile26.uf.tistory.com/image/211BD147525CA3A7027EFB\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>그리고, 끝까지 함께 해주신 재가불자들</p><p><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"428\" src=\"http://cfile29.uf.tistory.com/image/2215BC47525CA3A806D73A\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"428\" src=\"http://cfile4.uf.tistory.com/image/23769247525CA3A81BADA3\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"428\" src=\"http://cfile5.uf.tistory.com/image/270C7F47525CA3A80D447D\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"428\" src=\"http://cfile3.uf.tistory.com/image/2158FF47525CA3A9317871\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"428\" src=\"http://cfile25.uf.tistory.com/image/211AA947525CA3A903B4D0\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"428\" src=\"http://cfile24.uf.tistory.com/image/224DB147525CA3A939CF80\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"428\" src=\"http://cfile8.uf.tistory.com/image/246A1F37525CA3AA2950BB\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"428\" src=\"http://cfile23.uf.tistory.com/image/276BAC37525CA3AA2C3F13\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"428\" src=\"http://cfile9.uf.tistory.com/image/227C5937525CA3AA1E9928\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"428\" src=\"http://cfile28.uf.tistory.com/image/2661B237525CA3AB306AF4\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span class=\"imageblock\" style=\"width: 640px; height: auto; display: inline-block;\"><img width=\"640\" height=\"428\" src=\"http://cfile22.uf.tistory.com/image/2212D337525CA3AB0E219C\"></span></p>", visible: false, anonymous: false},
  {intab_id: 9, author_name: "관리자", author_id: 1, author_passwd: "bsr213417", title: "재가불자 10월 선언, 기자간담회 개최", file1: nil, file2: nil, ir1: "<!--StartFragment--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 맑은 고딕; font-size: 11pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 맑은 고딕;\"><!--StartFragment--><p class=\"0\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 155%; margin-left: 10pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 맑은 고딕;\">교단자정센터에서는 지난 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 맑은 고딕; font-size: 11pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 맑은 고딕;\">23</span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 맑은 고딕;\">일 이사회를 통해 총무원장 선거에 대한 평가와 향후 재가불자들과 함께할 수 있는 방안들에 대해 논의하였습니다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 맑은 고딕; font-size: 11pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 맑은 고딕;\">.<br></span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 맑은 고딕;\">그&nbsp;결과의 첫 번째로 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 맑은 고딕; font-size: 11pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 맑은 고딕;\">10</span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 맑은 고딕;\">월 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 맑은 고딕; font-size: 11pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 맑은 고딕;\">31</span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 맑은 고딕;\">일 기자간담회를 통해 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 맑은 고딕; font-size: 11pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 맑은 고딕;\">‘</span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 맑은 고딕;\">법리적 관점에서 분석한 제</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 맑은 고딕; font-size: 11pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 맑은 고딕;\">34</span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 맑은 고딕;\">대 총무원장 선거과정과 결과 설명</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 맑은 고딕; font-size: 11pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 맑은 고딕;\">’</span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 맑은 고딕;\">과 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 맑은 고딕; font-size: 11pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 맑은 고딕;\">‘</span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 맑은 고딕;\">청정한 출재가 종도들이 함께 새로운 교단문화</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 맑은 고딕; font-size: 11pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 맑은 고딕;\">, </span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 맑은 고딕;\">재가불자 운동 선언</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 맑은 고딕; font-size: 11pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 맑은 고딕;\">’</span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 맑은 고딕;\">하고 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 맑은 고딕; font-size: 11pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 맑은 고딕;\">‘</span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 맑은 고딕;\">재가불자 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 맑은 고딕; font-size: 11pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 맑은 고딕;\">10</span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 맑은 고딕;\">월 선언문</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 맑은 고딕; font-size: 11pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 맑은 고딕;\">’</span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 맑은 고딕;\">을 발표했습니다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 맑은 고딕; font-size: 11pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 맑은 고딕;\">. <br></span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 맑은 고딕;\">이날 기자간담회를 통해 교구종회에서 본사주지 등에게 총무원장 선거인단 선출을 위임한 행위는 선거법에 위반된다며 총무원장 자승스님은 직선제를 위한 종헌개정을 완수하고 임기와 상관없이 물러나야 함을 밝혔습니다.</span><br>그리고 재가불자 운동으로 범계행위에 연루된 사찰에 대해 보시하지 않고, 특히 그 곳이 문화재 관람료를 받는 사찰이라면 관람료 내지 않는 등의 활동을 제안했습니다.<br>끝으로 11월 28일 현행 선거법의 문제점과 개정 방향 등을 논의하는 토론회를&nbsp;개최할 계획을 알렸습니다.</p></span><p class=\"0\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 155%; margin-left: 10pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>", visible: false, anonymous: false},
