  {intab_id: 9, author_name: "관리자", author_id: 1, author_passwd: "bsr213417", title: "‘붓다 스터디’ 개척자 학교 안내", file1: nil, file2: nil, ir1: "<p><br>&nbsp;</p><p class=\"0\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; line-height: 130%; -ms-word-break: keep-all; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: -0.6pt; font-family: 문체부 제목 바탕체; font-size: 36pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 문체부 제목 바탕체; mso-font-width: 94%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">‘</span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: -0.6pt; font-size: 36pt; mso-font-width: 94%; mso-fareast-font-family: 문체부 제목 바탕체;\">붓다 스터디</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: -0.6pt; font-family: 문체부 제목 바탕체; font-size: 36pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 문체부 제목 바탕체; mso-font-width: 94%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">’ </span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: -0.6pt; font-size: 36pt; mso-font-width: 94%; mso-fareast-font-family: 문체부 제목 바탕체;\">개척자 학교</span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; line-height: 130%; -ms-word-break: keep-all; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 한컴 바겐세일 B; font-size: 18pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 한컴 바겐세일 B; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\"><br><br>Buddha-Parisa-Sati</span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 18pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 문체부 제목 바탕체;\">로 </span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: -0.6pt; font-size: 18pt; mso-font-width: 94%; mso-fareast-font-family: 문체부 제목 바탕체;\">새로운 개척시대를 연다</span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; margin-top: 15pt; -ms-word-break: keep-all; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 13pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 문체부 제목 바탕체;\">그 길을 작은 등불로 밝히며</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 문체부 제목 바탕체; font-size: 13pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 문체부 제목 바탕체; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 13pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 문체부 제목 바탕체;\">부처님 생애를 새로이 공부한다</span></p><!--StartFragment--><p class=\"0\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; margin-top: 6pt; -ms-word-break: keep-all; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 1pt; font-size: 20pt; font-weight: bold; mso-font-width: 110%; mso-fareast-font-family: 문체부 제목 바탕체;\">사단법인 불교아카데미</span></p><p><br><!--StartFragment--></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin-top: 6pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 13pt; font-weight: bold; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조; mso-hansi-font-family: 한양신명조;\">▣ </span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 13pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조;\">개척자 학교를 여는 취지</span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 140%; margin-top: 13pt; margin-left: 10pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조;\">높은 산 험한 물 황량한 들판</span><br><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조;\">극한의 추위와 더위</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 한양신명조; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 한양신명조; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\"><font face=\"굴림\">, </font></span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조;\">사나운 도적들</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 한양신명조; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 한양신명조; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\"><font face=\"굴림\">, </font></span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조;\">독사들</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 한양신명조; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 한양신명조; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\"><font face=\"굴림\">, </font></span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조;\">맹수들</span><br><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조;\">집요한 박해</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 한양신명조; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 한양신명조; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\"><font face=\"굴림\">, </font></span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조;\">끊임없는 갈등과 내부 분열 </span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조; mso-hansi-font-family: 한양신명조;\">―</span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 140%; margin-top: 13pt; margin-left: 10pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조;\">그 모든 것을 이겨내고</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 한양신명조; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 한양신명조; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\"><font face=\"굴림\">, </font></span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조;\">극복하고</span><br><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 한양신명조; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 한양신명조; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\"><font face=\"굴림\">‘</font></span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조;\">붓다의 신천지</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 한양신명조; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 한양신명조; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\"><font face=\"굴림\">’</font></span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조;\">를 열어가는 부처님과 초기대중들 </span><br><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조; mso-hansi-font-family: 한양신명조;\">― </span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: -0.2pt; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-font-width: 98%; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조;\">상인들</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: -0.2pt; font-family: 한양신명조; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 한양신명조; mso-font-width: 98%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\"><font face=\"굴림\">, </font></span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: -0.2pt; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-font-width: 98%; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조;\">기업가들</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: -0.2pt; font-family: 한양신명조; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 한양신명조; mso-font-width: 98%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\"><font face=\"굴림\">, </font></span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: -0.2pt; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-font-width: 98%; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조;\">노동자들</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: -0.2pt; font-family: 한양신명조; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 한양신명조; mso-font-width: 98%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\"><font face=\"굴림\">, </font></span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: -0.2pt; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-font-width: 98%; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조;\">지식인들</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: -0.2pt; font-family: 한양신명조; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 한양신명조; mso-font-width: 98%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\"><font face=\"굴림\">, </font></span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: -0.2pt; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-font-width: 98%; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조;\">정치인들</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: -0.2pt; font-family: 한양신명조; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 한양신명조; mso-font-width: 98%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\"><font face=\"굴림\">, </font></span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: -0.2pt; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-font-width: 98%; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조;\">군인들</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: -0.2pt; font-family: 한양신명조; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 한양신명조; mso-font-width: 98%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\"><font face=\"굴림\">, </font></span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: -0.2pt; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-font-width: 98%; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조;\">여성들</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: -0.2pt; font-family: 한양신명조; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 한양신명조; mso-font-width: 98%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\"><font face=\"굴림\">, </font></span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: -0.2pt; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-font-width: 98%; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조;\">수행자들</span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 140%; margin-top: 13pt; margin-left: 10pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조;\">그 거친 개척정신</span><br><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조;\">바로 이것이 초기불교 성공의 역동적인 동력</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 한양신명조; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 한양신명조; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\"><font face=\"굴림\">(</font></span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조;\">動力</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 한양신명조; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 한양신명조; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\"><font face=\"굴림\">)</font></span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조;\">이다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 한양신명조; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 한양신명조; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\"><font face=\"굴림\">.</font></span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 140%; margin-top: 13pt; margin-left: 10pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조;\">함께 모여 공부하는 것이 거의 유일한 출구이다</span><font face=\"굴림\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 한양신명조; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 한양신명조; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">.</span><br></font><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조;\">빠리사</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 한양신명조; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 한양신명조; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\"><font face=\"굴림\">(Parisa) </font></span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조; mso-hansi-font-family: 한양신명조;\">― </span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조;\">다섯 명이든 열 명이든 평등하게 둘러</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 한양신명조; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 한양신명조; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\"><font face=\"굴림\">(pari) </font></span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조;\">앉아</span><font face=\"굴림\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 한양신명조; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 한양신명조; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">(sa)</span><br></font><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조;\">붓다의 그 거친 개척의 삶을 공부하는 것</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 한양신명조; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 한양신명조; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\"><font face=\"굴림\">!</font></span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 140%; margin-top: 13pt; margin-left: 10pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조;\">팔십 평생 낡은 수레처럼 무너져 내리면서도 멈추지 않고</span><br><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: -0.2pt; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-font-width: 98%; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조;\">열반의 마지막 순간까지 숲속 외진 마을 가난한 이들 찾아가 법을 설하신</span><br><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조;\">붓다 석가모니의 그 거친 개척의 삶을 배우고 익히고 닮아가는 것</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 한양신명조; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 한양신명조; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\"><font face=\"굴림\">!</font></span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 140%; margin-top: 13pt; margin-left: 10pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shapetype id=\"_x0000_t75\" coordsize=\"21600,21600\" o:spt=\"75\" o:preferrelative=\"t\" path=\"m@4@5l@4@11@9@11@9@5xe\" filled=\"f\" stroked=\"f\"> <v:stroke joinstyle=\"miter\"/> <v:formulas> <v:f eqn=\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\"/> <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 1 0\"/> <v:f eqn=\"sum 0 0 @1\"/> <v:f eqn=\"prod @2 1 2\"/> <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelWidth\"/> <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelHeight\"/> <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 0 1\"/> <v:f eqn=\"prod @6 1 2\"/> <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelWidth\"/> <v:f eqn=\"sum @8 21600 0\"/> <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelHeight\"/> <v:f eqn=\"sum @10 21600 0\"/> </v:formulas> <v:path o:extrusionok=\"f\" gradientshapeok=\"t\" o:connecttype=\"rect\"/> <o:lock v:ext=\"edit\" aspectratio=\"t\"/> </v:shapetype><v:shape id=\"_x162150824\" style=\"v-text-anchor:top;mso-position-vertical-relative:line;mso-position-vertical:absolute;margin-top:30.87pt;mso-position-horizontal-relative:text;mso-position-horizontal:absolute;margin-left:314.61pt;width:138.95pt;height:170.07pt;position:absolute;\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"><v:imagedata o:title=\"EMB00000e24147f\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\bsr-002\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\Hnc\\BinData\\EMB00000e24147f.bmp\"/><w:wrap type=\"square\"/></v:shape><![endif]--><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조;\">내가 </span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조; mso-hansi-font-family: 한양신명조;\">― </span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조;\">우리가 </span><br><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조;\">부처님같이 그 거친 개척자로 다시 일어서는 것</span><font face=\"굴림\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 한양신명조; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 한양신명조; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">!</span><br></font><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조;\">이것이 위기의 우리 불교 다시 살려내는 </span><br><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조;\">거의 유일한 출구이며 살길이다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 한양신명조; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 한양신명조; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\"><font face=\"굴림\">.</font></span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 140%; margin-top: 13pt; margin-left: 10pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: -0.2pt; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-font-width: 98%; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조;\">이것이 길잃고 방황하는 우리 동포를 살려내는</span><br><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조;\">거의 유일한 출구이며 살길이다</span><font face=\"굴림\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 한양신명조; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 한양신명조; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">.</span><br></font><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조;\">아니</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 한양신명조; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 한양신명조; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\"><font face=\"굴림\">, </font></span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조;\">이것이 바로 나 자신을 살려내는 </span><br><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조;\">거의 유일한 출구이며 살길이다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 한양신명조; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 한양신명조; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\"><font face=\"굴림\">.</font></span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 140%; margin-top: 13pt; margin-left: 10pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조;\">개척자 학교 </span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조; mso-hansi-font-family: 한양신명조;\">―</span><br><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조;\">이것은 우리를 놀랍게 변화시킬 것이다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 한양신명조; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 한양신명조; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\"><font face=\"굴림\">. </font></span></p><p><font face=\"굴림\"><br><!--StartFragment--></font></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 140%; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 13pt; font-weight: bold; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조; mso-hansi-font-family: 한양신명조;\">▣ </span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 13pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조;\">제</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 한양신명조; font-size: 13pt; font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 한양신명조; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\"><font face=\"굴림\">1</font></span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 13pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 한양신명조;\">기 기초과정 수강생 모집</span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 140%; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]-->&nbsp;<!--[endif]--> <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 140%; margin-left: 5pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 한양신명조; font-size: 11pt; font-weight: bold;\"></spa