-hansi-font-family: 나눔고딕;\">&nbsp; &#8226; </span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 나눔고딕;\">주요안건 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 나눔고딕; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 나눔고딕;\">: </span></p><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 나눔고딕; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 나눔고딕;\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; 1. 2014년 사업평가 및 결산보고</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;2. 2015년 사업계획 및 예산 심의</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 3. 이사장 선출 및 신임 원장 인선의 건</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 4.&nbsp;신임 이사 영입의 건</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 5.&nbsp;기타 안건</span></p></span><p style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 180%; margin-left: 0pt; -ms-layout-grid-mode: both; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><br></span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">※ 2월&nbsp;정기법회&nbsp;후에 이사회를 진행할 예정입니다.</span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><br></span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: 나눔고딕; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 나눔고딕;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&