: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">사진출전 네오룩</span></p><p><br></p></span><p><br></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"line-height: 180%; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">이 두 병풍 사진을 대조한 결과 아래 기재한 </span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">가지 이유로 흥국사 </span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">‘</span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">십장생 병풍</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">’</span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">과의 연관성을 추정해 볼 수 있었다</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">.</span></p><p><br></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"line-height: 180%; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움;\">&nbsp; </span></p><p><br></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"line-height: 180%; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">1) </span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">둘 다 조선 후기에 제작되었다고 함</span></p><p><br></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"line-height: 180%; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">2) 20</span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">년대 촬영 십장생 병풍은 사람 키로 추장하면 </span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">미터가 넘는 것으로 보임</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">. </span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">국민대 전시 병풍이 </span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">349Cm</span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">로 측정된 것을 고려하면</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">두 병풍의 크기는 거의 비슷하게 보임</span></p><p><br></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"line-height: 180%; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">3) </span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">십장생 병풍이 통상 </span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">8</span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">폭 혹은 </span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">10</span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">폭으로 제작되는 데 이 병풍은 모두 </span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">폭으로 제작되어 있음</span></p><p><br></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"line-height: 180%; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">4) </span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">병풍제작을 위해 그림이 절개된 부분이 동일하게 보임</span></p><p><br></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"line-height: 180%; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움;\">&nbsp; </span></p><p><br></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"line-height: 180%; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">특히 병풍 제작을 위해 그림을 절개한 부위를 대조해 보면 완전히 동일한 위치에서 절개되어</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">병풍으로 제작되어 있다는 점을 확인해 볼 수 있다</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">. </span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">그렇다면 국민대 병풍은 흥국사 병풍과 동일품이거나 혹은 흥국사 병풍을 모본으로 그려진 병풍일 수 밖에 없다는 판단을 내릴 수 밖에 없다</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">. 1977</span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">년 사라진 흥국사 제 </span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">의 보물 십장생 병풍의 실존 가능성을 찾아낸 순간이었다</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">.(</span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">별첨</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">1 </span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">사진 참조</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">)</span></p><p><br></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"line-height: 180%; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움;\">&nbsp; </span></p><p><br></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"line-height: 180%; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">4. </span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">국민대 전시회 작품은 모사품일 가능성이 농후</span></p><p><br></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"line-height: 180%; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움;\">&nbsp; </span></p><p><br></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"line-height: 180%; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">국내의 대표적인 한국화가이자 고서화 전문가에게 사진 판독을 부탁한 결과</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">조선시대 작품으로 보기에는 나무를 표현한 색채가 탁하며 조선시대에 사용된 석채</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">(</span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">혹은 암채</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">)</span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">로 색채가 되었으면 보다 붉은 색깔을 띠었을 것이다</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">구름의 서기</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">(</span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">영롱한 기운</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">) </span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">표현이 부족하다</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">전체적으로 그림에서 표현하고자 하는 작가의 긴장감이 보이지 않으며</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">바위의 선표현이 복잡하고 학에 대한 표현이 모사한 것으로 보인다라는 평가가 나왔습니다</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">.</span></p><p><br></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"line-height: 180%; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움;\">&nbsp; </span></p><p><br></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"line-height: 180%; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">또한 위 사진을 돋보기로 자세힌 살펴본 결과 해의 위치</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">나무의 방향에서도 미세한 차이가 보였다</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">.</span></p><p><br></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"line-height: 180%; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움;\">&nbsp; </span></p><p><br></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"line-height: 180%; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">따라서 국민대 전시회 작품은 흥국사 시왕전에 걸려있는 사자탱화와 같이</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">진품을 보고 그린 모사품으로 일응 추측된다</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">.</span></p><p><br></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"line-height: 180%; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움;\">&nbsp; </span></p><p><br></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"line-height: 180%; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">5. </span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">흥국사 병풍을 현상 수배한다</span></p><p><br></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"line-height: 180%; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움;\">&nbsp; </span></p><p><br></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"line-height: 180%; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">흥국사 병풍은 언제 사라진 것일까</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">? </span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">현재로서는 </span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">1977</span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">년 작성된 봉선사의 공식 조사기록 </span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">‘</span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">봉선본말사약지</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">’</span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">의 기록을 토대로 그 이후임을 유추할 수 밖에 없다</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">. </span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 돋움;\">『</span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">전통사찰총서</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 돋움;\">』</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">5 </span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">인천</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">·</span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">경기도 전통사찰 </span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 돋움;\">Ⅱ</span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">의 내용상 </span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">1990</span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">년 초반 이내 임</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">(</span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">다시 공식보고서가 작성된 </span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">2004</span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">년 이내 임은 확실하다</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">)</span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">을 추측할 수 있다</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">. 1977</span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">년 이후 어느 시점에 사라진 흥국사의 보물 십장생 병풍은 </span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">2005</span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">년 국민대 박물관 도록에 기재된 기록에 의해 환수의 가능성이 엿보이기 시작했다</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">. </span></p><p><br></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"line-height: 180%; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">그렇다면 남은 과제는 첫째</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">국민대 도록에 게재된 사진의 출처와 소장자가 누구인지를 찾아 내는 일이다</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">.</span></p><p><br></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"line-height: 180%; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">둘째</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">소장자에게 모사품이었다면 모사의 대상이 되었던 원본은 어떻게 구했는지</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">병풍의 작가는 누구인지를 질의하여 유통경로를 확인하고</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">원본의 소재지를 파악하여야 한다</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">.</span></p><p><br></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"line-height: 180%; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">셋째</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">유통경로 확인을 통하여 병풍이 어떻게 유출되었는 지를 확인하여</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">흥국사로 하여금 원본을 되찾게 하여야 한다</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">.</span></p><p><br></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"line-height: 180%; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움;\">&nbsp; </span></p><p><br></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"line-height: 180%; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">현재 국민대 박물관에는 모사품으로 보이는 십장생병풍이 존재하지 않는다고 한다</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">. </span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">죽 국민대 박물관 소장품이 아니다</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">. </span></p><p><br></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"line-height: 180%; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">우리 탱화반환대책위는 위 모사품으로 보이는 십장생병풍과 유사한 그림을 확보하여 똑같은 화가가 그렸는 지 여부를 확인하려 하였고</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">천신만고 끝에 유사한 그림을 확보하여 판독을 의뢰하려하였으나</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">똑같은 화가가 그렸는 지 여부는 판독이 불가능하다는 결론을 얻었다</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">.</span></p><p><br></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"line-height: 180%; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움;\">&nbsp; </span></p><p><br></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"line-height: 180%; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">따라서 우리는 십장생병풍을 흥국사로 온전히 환수하기 위하여 현상금을 걸고 수배하고자 한다</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">.</span></p><p><br></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"line-height: 180%; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움;\">&nbsp; </span></p><p><br></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"line-height: 180%; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">위 모사품으로 보이는 십장생병풍의 원본그림의 소재자 내지는 소재지에 대한 정보를 제공하는 사람에게 사례금으로 </span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">500</span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">만원을 제공한다</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">.</span></p><p><br></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"line-height: 180%; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움;\">&nbsp; </span></p><p><br></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"line-height: 180%; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움;\">&nbsp; </span></p><p><br></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"line-height: 180%; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">별첨 </span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">1. </span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">흥국사 </span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">/</span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">국민대 십장생 병풍 비교사진</span></p><p><br></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"line-height: 180%; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">별첨 </span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">2. </span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">봉선사 본말사 약지</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">(</span><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">표지 및 흥국사편 </span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">P20)</span></p><p><br></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"line-height: 180%; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움;\">&nbsp; </span></p><p><br></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 180%; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움;\">&nbsp; </span></p><p><br></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 180%; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">2015. 12. 30.</span></p><p><br></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 180%; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움;\">&nbsp; </span></p><p><br></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 180%; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움;\">&nbsp; </span></p><p><br></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 180%; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움; font-size: 20pt; font-weight: bold; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">흥국사 도난탱화반환대책위원회</span></p><p><br></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"line-height: 180%; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움;\">&nbsp; </span></p><p><br></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"line-height: 180%; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Dotum,돋움;\">&nbsp; </span></p><p><br></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"line-height: 180%; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"line-height: 180%; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">별첨 </span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">1. </span><span style=\"font-family: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">흥국사 </span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 돋움; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt;\">/</span><span style=\"font-family: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 돋움;\">국민대 십장생 병풍 비교사진</span></p><p><br></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"line-height: 180%